			<h2>Correspondence</h2>
			<a class="xsmall link-alt" href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">Write a Letter to the Editor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>
		</div>

		<div id="article-correspondences" class="correspondences correspondences-collapsed">
								<div class="block-correspondence" id="804">
		<blockquote class="quote-2">
			<p>Brian Doyle&rsquo;s short prose piece &ldquo;<a href="/article/4506">The Hawk</a>&rdquo; [February 2011] is a tiny literary jewel that I will share with as many friends and acquaintances as possible. The story he tells gives me great comfort and validates my belief in the potential for good in the world.</p>
							<p class="quote-2-author">David Bagnard<br>Garden Valley, Idaho</p>
					</blockquote>
	</div>

					</div>

			</div>
    
